data.description: Escape to this custom-built 5 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom rural retreat on 4.5 acres just outside Mountain Home city limits. Mesmerizing mountain vistas surround this property, complemented by a meandering dry creek bed. Inside, enjoy plush upgraded carpets and luxury vinyl plank flooring, freshly painted walls, and upgraded lighting fixtures. The kitchen features upgraded countertops, and a new water heater ensures convenience. Relax in the spacious living area or entertain to your heart's desire in the inviting family room. Outdoors, a covered front porch and expansive back deck offer picturesque settings. Pear trees dot the landscape, providing fresh fruit. This property includes a tool shed, storage trailer, and a John Deere lawn mower for easy maintenance. Embrace country living with modern luxuries in this idyllic retreat.
